result.name: isles-of-scilly-subtidal-biotope-map
result.notes: Study to map the extent of the subtidal sediment habitat around the Isles of Scilly from mean low water down to around the 50m depth contour, with most effort concentrated >30m. Acoustic mapping and ground-truthing by grab-sampling and drop-down video, together with aerial photographs.
